Stroll through Kalama Park, less than a mile away, take a surf lesson at the famous Cove Park, or enjoy tennis on one of 6 onsite courts. The area's vibrant walking community gives you easy access to cafes, restaurants, shopping, and nightlife, making this an ideal location for experiencing Maui's island lifestyle. Don't miss this opportunity to own a turnkey beach retreat in one of Maui's most sought-after locations!
